{"tid":466028,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"卡巴斯基創辦人自爆：曾經複製使用者電腦上與病毒無關的檔案！","createTime":"2017-11-12T07:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T17:49:04.000Z","uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"66e130c7c53aaa4774e28546145cf6173c6a0926","tid":466028,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:09:39.000Z","msg":"美國國土安全部曾發公告表示，要完全封殺防毒軟體卡巴斯基（Kaspersky），原因是懷疑卡巴斯基曾協助俄羅斯情報單位透過管道竊取機密資訊。卡巴斯基雖否認，但根據科技媒體 CNET 最新報導，事情的最新發展是，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>卡巴斯基創辦人 Eugene Kaspersky 日前承認，曾在使用者電腦複製和病毒無關的檔案<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</strong></span></span>消費者震驚之餘，也開始質疑該防毒軟體的安全性。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/05092353/170533626_1e9de69dda_o-624x468.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F05092353%2F170533626_1e9de69dda_o-624x468.jpg&h=2b003226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://finance.technews.tw/2017/11/06/kaspersky-copy-data-from-user/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffinance.technews.tw%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2Fkaspersky-copy-data-from-user%2F&d=9rRABI4mxnU312pk21FbRAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=241422d9\" target=\"_blank\">http://finance.technews.tw/2017/11/06/kaspersky-copy-data-from-user/</a></div>"},{"pid":"da8c252a33f598351b93aa8f4449e5691d185611","tid":466028,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:10:47.000Z","msg":"報導指出，Eugene Kaspersky 雖然沒有透露更多細節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，例如他們從使用者電腦複製了什麼檔案<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，複製檔案之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，曾用來執行什麼工作等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。依照程序，這必須要獲得用戶同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但顯然卡巴斯基違反了規定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。但卡巴斯基強調，他們此舉只是為了找到網路罪犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"8168e5c143acb1a461c0d167641404504f658bba","tid":466028,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:14:14.000Z","msg":"卡巴斯基防毒軟體屢遭質疑有安全程序問題後，不但在美國遭到聯邦政府封殺，零售商店也遭下架。包括美國最大電子產品實體零售店 Best Buy 已將軟體下架停售<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，理由是「太多疑問未解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」。另一商店 Office Depot 也跟進宣布，將卡巴斯基的產品下架停售<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"9b6b510528fd295e4adb9c00678b5eaf99b610b1","tid":466028,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:14:49.000Z","msg":"之前《紐約時報》報導指出，以色列情報人員入侵卡巴斯基網路逾兩年，發現俄政府駭客盜取一名美國國家安全局（NSA）僱員儲存在家中電腦的國防機密文件，而該電腦正好安裝了卡巴斯基防毒軟體。因俄羅斯情報機構聯邦安全局（FSB）有能力存取卡巴斯基客戶的資料庫及原始碼。因此，俄羅斯駭客有能力藉此向美國政府及企業發動網路攻擊。不過，目前不清楚俄方透過卡巴斯基防毒軟體掌握多少美國國家機密，而以色列也將此通知華府。"},{"pid":"89e45a5248a4ff59ffd425bb8e391eb59fc31064","tid":466028,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:15:06.000Z","msg":"此事嚴重衝擊卡巴斯基防毒軟體的信譽，卡巴斯基為了自清，日前宣布全球透明度計畫（Global Transparency Initiatives），在 2018 年第 1 季前公開產品程式碼及程式設計作業方式給獨立機構檢視，還砸重金邀研究人員幫忙抓漏。只是，這項自清行動才宣布沒多久，創辦人 Eugene Kaspersky 又自爆，曾經在使用者電腦複製和病毒無關的檔案事件。這些諸多疑點如果不能一一釐清，恐怕將難以挽回各界對卡巴斯基防毒軟體的信心。"},{"pid":"64ff965879e6238a8349ec80ec4f9eaaa7635509","tid":466028,"uid":34383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:16:30.000Z","msg":"開唔開成龍事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd16bfecdd601a3395b233a555243bbdd7b69b75","tid":466028,"uid":34383,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:16:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關唔關成龍事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2fcca3784e7ac275ac6f784917aa5199b6a03554","tid":466028,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:24:16.000Z","msg":"裝防毒同裝病毒無分別<br />\n－－<br />\n《朋友名言》"},{"pid":"f8718beeb7e1f6f9dc28ba3b1e71d1d9a93adfbe","tid":466028,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:04:20.000Z","msg":"linux開心用家路過"},{"pid":"7670f800b9dc93c6b25e4f6e7952e8b5ef068e5d","tid":466028,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:33:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>linux開心用家路過</blockquote><br />\nbitdefender用家開心路過"},{"pid":"1448cc16063e220ba1d015b2b403e331dda5bcf3","tid":466028,"uid":73231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:45:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>linux開心用家路過</blockquote><br />\n工力口力口力豖者口牙"},{"pid":"765cdb55bae2823ac0f114665510f89386b80c88","tid":466028,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:54:30.000Z","msg":"雞巴司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8c212bd54c4b659c04105ab32c918947769cd4","tid":466028,"uid":26106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:54:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>linux開心用家路過</blockquote><br />\n你老母個西用家路過"},{"pid":"eb6db28cfb8f09becb0b84075dadc156cc91095d","tid":466028,"uid":47701,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/12/191129_70e163b25169801866551f65b8c7e617.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F12%2F191129_70e163b25169801866551f65b8c7e617.jpg&h=f003dee2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a50a3122f4e8dad45109f20067ad2291978d14e2","tid":466028,"uid":153811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T1